Change port in prefs to take effect immediately
Make ANON connections automatic
Put more possible things to watch in the main window, but let client choose what to show
Possibly make prefs use seperate windows for editing each user/group
Notify needed to get done soon (per command?)
Helpfile in printable form (ps?)

@endnode
